ConverterTests - Class in coretest
This class converts executes for each given UmlInputRepresentation with its corresponding UmlRepresentationConverter the tests for each of the following converters:
UmlCodeConverter

To add a new sample diagram representation to the test suite, the input file has to be added to the resources-folder and the UmlInputRepresentation and UmlRepresentationConverter have to be added to the parameter array in ConverterTests.data().
